==English==
===Noun===
'''tooth fairy'''

# a figure of modern [[myth]] said to give children a small amount of money (or sometimes a present) in exchange for a [[tooth]] when it falls out of the [[deciduous]] [[dentition]].  An imaginary creature, believed to exist mostly by children and the unsophistocated, not unlike a belief in the [[Easter Bunny]], [[Santa Claus]] or [[Jesus Christ]].

